headline: One Winner, or Maybe Two or Three
abstract: O.K., maybe there will be a clear winner on Monday night. But let me explain what else might happen.
lead_paragraph: AMES, Iowa — Driving through the snowy cornfields of Iowa today, I couldn’t stop dreaming about next Tuesday, the day after the Iowa caucuses. After more than a year of campaign entrances and exits, debates and dance moves, we’ll finally get some real clarity about this crowded Democratic primary race.
